data.description: Check out this centrally located 3 bedroom 2 bath. This home sits in a quiet neighborhood. The home boasts tile floors throughout the main living areas and carpeting in bedrooms. The kitchen has been updated with new white shaker cabinets and granite countertops as well as stainless steel appliances. The home has an open floor plan with a formal dining room, lots of natural light, a covered lanai overlooking the fenced backyard, a washer and dryer are included as well as an extra refrigerator in the 2-car garage. THE ROOF WAS REPLACED 2022!
